flowRoot.flowPara: As a "Lie detector" but mostly to distract from the survey and the attempt to read out private thoughts and emotions ...

Sold as a "phantasy test with formless blobs for children, normal adults and for mentally ill", in fact it distracts the questioned (fixation 1), with a simple RFID or LC circuit stuck on the backside of the paper it's also possible to activate small Active Denial Systems, Hum Noises or treble Sounds arround 15'000Hz below the conscious perception threshold (fixation 2...)
